text: Chesnokovka () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Chesnokovsky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 3,333 as of 2010. There are 83 streets. == Geography == It is located 12 km from Ufa. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Chesnokovka, Republic of Bashkortostan
